INSTALATION

in your project directory run:
git submodule add git@github.com:appunite/gtm-oauth2.git Frameworks/GTMOAuth2

drag Frameworks/GTMOAuth2/Source/GTMOAuth2.xcodeproj to your project

add OAuthTouchStaticLib (GTMOAuth2) to "Target Dependencies"
add libOAuthTouch2.a to "Link Binary With Libraries"
add "$(SOURCE_ROOT)/Frameworks/GTMOAuth2/Source/Build"
  and "$(SOURCE_ROOT)/Frameworks/GTMOAuth2/Source/Frameworks/GTMHTTPFetcher/Source/Build"
  to "Header Search Paths"

